    "message": "refactor(ui): convert `AccountListAdapter` to Kotlin and migrate to `RecyclerView`\n\n- Rewrite `AccountListAdapter` in Kotlin and migrate from `ListView` to `RecyclerView.Adapter` using ViewBinding\n- Replace `ListView` with `RecyclerView` in `ui_account.xml` and update `AccountUI.java` logic accordingly\n- Refactor `item_account.xml` layout to use constraints for action buttons and add a new \"copy UUID\" button\n- Improve UI responsiveness by using `View.INVISIBLE` instead of `View.GONE` for progress indicators to maintain layout stability\n- Update `AccountUI` to properly initialize `LinearLayoutManager` and refresh the adapter's data set using a list of `AccountListItem` objects",
